SUMMARY:Wine & Paint Saturday Night
DESCRIPTION:Get your favorite people together and join us for a Wine & Paint Saturday Night.\nPaint along with us. We‘ll guide you through the entire project.  All supplies provided and one glass of wine, bottle of beer, latte or cup of coffee included in your project fee. (Other non-alcoholic beverages are also available for substitution.) Must be 21+ to participate in this activity.\n
