SUMMARY:Rock Fest 2026
DESCRIPTION:Join the Brown County Rock and Mineral Club at the Nature Center as we take a look at some amazing rock displays and learn more about why geology rocks! This event will run from 11am-4pm in the shelter house at the Nature Center and will feature crafts for kids. There will be Gold Panning, Rock Painting, Geodes, Fossils, Minerals, and more!\nProgram schedule TBA.\n
