SUMMARY:Mammal Furs
DESCRIPTION:Did you know that not all fur is the same? Different animals use their fur for camoflauge, protection, and keeping warm in a variety of habitats. Visit the Nature Center to learn about Indiana’s native mammals. Learn about their habits, habitats, play a short game, and touch real animal furs!\n
