SUMMARY:Bourbon Festival (21+)
DESCRIPTION:During prohibition, moonshine was bootlegged out of Story such that Sheriff Clarence Moore captured the notorious still on site.  As the story goes, half of the ‘evidence’ went missing.  Story still celebrates the fermentation process by hosting public events.\nEnjoy local craft bourbon, live music & entertainment, with arts, crafts, and food vendors Saturday October 24, 2026.\nLeave the children at home for this age 21+ event.\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/bourbon-festival-21/
