SUMMARY:Stars, Stripes, and Story
DESCRIPTION:The Independence Day Concert and Fireworks Show evolved to include a fundraising dinner in support for the Brown County Community Foundation!\nLocal suppliers, farmers, and gardeners all chipped in to provide the ingredients.  When placed in the hands of our talented culinary team this fundraising dinner became possible!\n$3,972 was raised from the dinner sales, cash donations, and gift certificate sales.  This amount qualified for a double match from the Lilly Foundation which brought the total fundraising effort to $11,916.\nSpecial thanks to Lilly, local purveyors, and especially the Brown County Community Foundation for being the tether for so many incredible groups in the community.\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/stars-stripes-and-story/
