DESCRIPTION:Indiana Uplands Wine Country presents Cheese Lover’s Weekend on May 16 and 17!! Six of the wineries in the Indiana Uplands will be pairing cheese with wine for everyone who does a wine tasting. Brown County Winery will be serving Kenny’s Farmhouse Cheese with our wine. We will suggest the best options for each cheese with your wine tasting. Visit the Winery in Gnaw Bone and the other 5 wineries for a delicious wine and cheese weekend!\n(Cheese only at the winery location on Highway 46. Not every winery in IUWC is participating in the event.)\n
