SUMMARY:Goat Conspiracy SPRING FLING 5K and Porch Concert
DESCRIPTION:Spring has sprung! Join The Goat Conspiracy Sanctuary for our second awesome 5K Fun Run and Porch Concert. Includes self-guided visits with the goats!\nThe morning starts with a run through the fields of The Goat Conspiracy Sanctuary. Run or cheer the runners and then kick back with music from the Cabin Porch, with delicious eats and drinks from the Planted food truck and Heartwork Brewing.\nIf you’re just coming for the music, the Cabin Porch Concert starts at 11am.\nWe’re thrilled to be working with IU’s Bloomington Delta Music Club to bring their exciting energy to the Cabin. This year’s lineup includes:\n\nBruce and the Spillers: Bruce Helton – guitar, Brody Brown – guitar, Gus Brown – bass, Ryan Ososki – drums, Michael Clarke – keys, Delilah Seal – lead vocals, Rose Kory/backup and lead vocals, Trey Christiansen – backup and lead vocals\nSunnyside Down: Lily Macey and Rose Kory – vocals, Alec McLaren – guitar and vocals\nBadminton 3: Jonathan – drums, Dante – vocals/guitar, Indigo – vocals, Jordan – bass, Barrett – keys\nAlways Late: Sophia – vocals, Lily – vocals, Leila and Ella – guitar, Rita – bass, Parker – keys, Griffin – drums\n\nIf you’re running or cheering the 5K, registration and gates open at 9:00am. Feel free to contact info@thegoatconspiracy.org with questions.\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/goat-conspiracy-spring-fling-5k-and-porch-concert/
