SUMMARY:The Brown County Art Guild Presents: Art In the Garden – Countryside Blooms & Brushes 2026
DESCRIPTION:Experience the beauty of Art in the Garden – Countryside Blooms & Brushes!  \nAn unforgettable annual evening awaits in the heart of Brown County. Join the Guild Artist Members as they paint en plein air, capturing the beauty of the countryside & spring flowers in real time. Wander the Austin Historic Farm, savor delicious food & relax to the sounds of live music. Original artwork & pottery will be available for purchase.  It’s a celebration of art, nature, and community!    \n \nSaturday, May 30, 2026 \nJenny & Bill Austin’s Country Retreat  \n$100 per person  \n5 – 8 pm  \nLive Music \nHeavy hors d’oeuvres by Nashville House Catering & Cash Bar \nGuild Artist Demonstrations  \nPaintings & Pottery for Sale  \nParking on Site  \nRain or Shine  \nPurchase tickets in person at the Guild, call 812-988-6185 or online at: \nhttps://browncountyartguild.org/event/art-in-the-garden-countryside-blooms-brushes/ \n______________________________________________________________________ \n \nBrown County Art Guild – A not for profit organization located in the heart of downtown Nashville, Indiana.  On display throughout its galleries is a prized collection of historic paintings as well as current works for sale from regional award-winning member artists.  \n Also offered throughout the year are artist demonstrations, workshops, and special exhibits.   \n Gallery hours March through December 2026, Monday – Saturday, 11 – 5 and Sunday, 12 – 4 or by appointment. \nIf you would like more information, call 812.988.6185 or visit our web site https://browncountyartguild.org/ \n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/the-brown-county-art-guild-presents-art-in-the-garden-countryside-blooms-brushes-2026/
ORGANIZER;CN=Brown County Art Guild:MAILTO:admin@bcartguild.org
CATEGORIES:Art Events &amp; Exhibits,Family Friendly,Food &amp; Drink,Happening,Live Music,Spring
