SUMMARY:Artists, Writers & Readers Retreat
DESCRIPTION:Come spend a weekend at Waycross to work on new or in-progress projects. Bring supplies and set up throughout our campus, spending the days working independently or with others, however is most fruitful for your creative process. In the evenings, there will be space for sharing, collaborating, and asking for feedback.\n\n\nNovember 13-15, 2026\n\n\nCheck-in: 4-6pm\n\n\nCheck-out: 10am\n\n\n\n\nAges 21+\n\n\nProgram Rates\n\n\nAttendance cost is calculated during online registration, depending on your lodging selection. Rates are per person and include program fees, lodging and meals.\n\n\nConference Center – Single Occupancy: $350 per person\n\n\nConference Center – Double Occupancy: $280 per person\n\n\n\n\n\n\n
